This is Absolutely beautiful, creative, and full of musical depth in their own story!
Long saying short, its an incredible documentary! Iv seen my fair share of small 100 Gec documentarys and as a hardcore fan I can proudly say, None of them come to close to compete detaile from beginning in their childhood to who we know now as 100 Gecs today as this documentary does. This documentary in my personal opinion deserves to be played and official on Theatre screens across the country. All the details you had in this one documentary was more detailed than a single interview you can find on them as people on Google on Wiki. And the fact that you didnt just focus on Laura and Dylan was amazing! There were so many amazing artists that help Laura and Dylan on their path to success and find their way to the top, as you mentioned PC Music, Charlie XCX, AG Cook, Skrillex and many many more! If this isnt the OFFICIAL 100 Gecs documentary I honestly dont know what is! I am constantly amazed by how much research you put into this video! I hope this video blows up and maybe Laura and Dylan themselves will watch it! The credit given to them is incredible. Their individual stories and paths  to success are amazing! This documentary wasnt just a documentary on 100 Gecs it was a movie that really gets in between the cracks of who we know as 100 Gecs today. This documentary deserves a golden award of some sort cause this was a Beautiful story of 100 Gecs! 

100 Gecs / 100 Gecs
